{"word":"μεταβαίνω","slug":"μεταβαίνω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>μεταβαίνω</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:μετά\">μετά</a>, βαίνω</el> ‘walk, step’] ‘make a transfer from one place to another’, <b>go,</b> whether <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ pers.\">pers.</a> or thing: <b><a href='B:470 8:34'>Mt 8:34</a>; <a href='B:470 11:1'>11:1</a>; <a href='B:470 17:20'>17:20</a>; <a href='B:500 7:3'>J 7:3</a>; <a href='B:500 13:1'>13:1</a>; <a href='B:510 18:7'>Ac 18:7</a>; move <a href='B:490 10:7'>Lk 10:7</a>.</b> —In imagery, of transition from one condition to another <b><a href='B:500 5:24'>J 5:24</a>; <a href='B:690 3:14'>1 J 3:14</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:μετάβα\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:μεταβάλλω\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}